### 1) 试卷列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test/papers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### 上报学习进度（正确写法：参数跟在 URL 同一行）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/learn/my/progress/upsert?courseId=1&lessonId=1&progressPercent=60&status=LEARNING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### 2) 交卷（变量 token 方式）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paperId": 1,
  "answers": [0,0,2,1],
  "usedMin": 2
}

### 3) 我的成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test/my/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



